Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Summer Denim - Vintage White'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Summer Denim’ showcases a blank-slate palette on a fashion-forward edition of the classic silhouette. The upper replaces traditional canvas construction with washed denim in a Vintage White finish. Both the interior tongue and lining are covered in a multicolor floral print for a vibrant warm-weather touch. The high-top rests on a matching white platform midsole, featuring EVA cushioning for a comfortable ride.

Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase 'Summit White Dark Purple Dust'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase ‘Summit White Dark Purple Dust’ pairs a lightweight and breathable mesh build with open-access functionality. Traditional woven laces are replaced by a set of thin cord laces, easily secured with one hand and integrated into dark violet webbing straps for midfoot lockdown. On the medial side, a zipper runs the length of the eyestay, allowing the shoe to be quickly slipped on and off. The sneaker is placed atop a Nike React foam midsole, featuring a forefoot Zoom Air unit tuned for extra bounce with each step.

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'White Aurora Green'
Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Summer Spirit - Bright Poppy'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck 70 High ‘Summer Spirit’ projects a summer-ready refresh, highlighted by a vintage floral print on an organic canvas upper in Bright Poppy. Traditional winged stitching is applied to the tongue, featuring a throwback Chuck Taylor tag on the interior of the right shoe. Additional branding elements include a circular All Star ankle patch and a 1970s license plate at the back of the midsole, built with raised and shiny rubber sidewalls in keeping with the elevated Chuck 70 aesthetic.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Summer Spirit - Sun and Rainbow'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Summer Spirit’ treats the classic silhouette to a warm-weather makeover. The low-top makes use of an ivory-hued canvas upper with embroidered star and rainbow graphics for a DIY look and feel. Bold pops of color arrive via sun-ray graphics on the custom sockliner in pink, yellow and red. The lace-up is mounted on a towering platform midsole, featuring lightweight EVA cushioning for a smooth ride.

results.name: Naomi Osaka x Wmns NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo 'Fierce Purple'
results.story: Made for the championship tennis player, the Naomi Osaka x Nike women’s NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo ‘Fierce Purple’ carries a textile upper equipped with a Dynamic Fit system. The technology eliminates the space between the foot and the shoe, resulting in a supportive, second-skin fit. ‘Empowered’ is printed on the tongue tag, while Naomi’s personal logo adorns the heel. The low-top sits on a tonal foam midsole that works in tandem with a full-length Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone tread designed for hard court surfaces.

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'White Metallic Silver'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Zoom Pegasus 38 ‘White Metallic Silver’ updates the performance running shoe with a lightweight build stripped of all color. An integrated lacing system secures a breathable mesh upper, built with a plush tongue and a wider toe box for an extra-comfortable fit. A cropped and outlined Swoosh shines in metallic silver on the lateral side. The sneaker rides on a matching white Nike React midsole, fitted with a Zoom Air unit in the forefoot for springy cushioning.

Jordan 3 Retro A Ma Maniére (W)
results.story: The A Ma Maniére x women's Air Jordan 3 Retro SP ‘Raised By Women’ treats the iconic silhouette to a premium makeover. The Atlanta-based retailer dresses the mid-top in tumbled white leather, overlaid with soft grey suede at the collar, eyestay, heel and toe. Mismatched Jumpman and A Ma Maniére branding is embroidered on each tongue, featuring a quilted lining that’s repeated on the interior collar. A subtle cream hue is applied to the molded heel panel, decorated with an embossed Nike Air logo, and polyurethane midsole. Violet-colored detailing wraps around the heel, providing a contrasting pop of color.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 Grit 'Black Energy Glow'
Wmns Dunk Low Disrupt 'Sea Glass'
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low Disrupt ‘Sea Glass’ offers a modern, reconstructed take on the vintage silhouette. The all-leather upper pairs a white base with contrasting overlays in a subdued tan finish. A soft pink hue distinguishes the exposed-foam tongue, which combines with a leather pull tab at the heel for a DIY-inspired look. The low-top is mounted on a segmented platform midsole with wraparound stitch detailing. Underfoot, flex grooves in the rubber outsole deliver a smooth ride.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Summer Spirit - Sunflowers'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Summer Spirit’ updates the classic silhouette with a floral print designed with the warm-weather months in mind. The high-top carries an off-white canvas upper entirely covered in brown and yellow sunflowers. Standard Chuck details remain intact, including chrome eyelets, an All Star ankle patch and a reinforced rubber toe cap. Matching white rubber is used on the midsole, accented with contrasting black pinstripes and a Converse license plate.

results.name: Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Summer Spirit - Gold Dart'
Wmns Run Star Hike High 'Made With Love - White'
results.story: The Converse women’s Run Star Hike High ‘Made With Love’ delivers a handwritten message on the sneaker’s pristine white canvas upper. Both sides panels are marked with embroidered text that lets the wearer know the kicks are made with love, expressed via an embroidered heart in Bright Poppy. The vibrant hue is repeated on a One Star logo on the back heel, as well as the two-tone sawtooth outsole that underpins the exaggerated platform midsole.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Summer Denim - Denim'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Summer Denim’ applies a pastel blue finish to a radically reworked version of the classic silhouette. Open heel construction transforms the low-top sneaker into an easy-to-wear slip-on, crafted from washed denim and secured with traditional lace closure. A multicolor floral print is applied the Ortholite sockliner and interior lining, enhancing the shoe’s summery aesthetic.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Camo'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Camo’ layers on multiple archive prints on a sustainable build. Leopard-print laces secure a 100% recycled poly-canvas upper, covered in a brown and green camo print and translucent zebra stripes. Additional leopard spots land on the sneaker’s heel overlay. The high-top rests on an off-white rubber midsole, supported underfoot by a standard Chuck outsole in brown rubber.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Vintage Floral'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Vintage Floral’ transforms the foundational sneaker with a summer-ready all-over print and a retooled design. The high-top carries a traditional canvas upper entirely covered in pink, crimson and orange blossoms. The ornate pattern is offset by a reinforced rubber toe cap and platform midsole, both rendered in a subtle off-white finish. A diamond-tread brown rubber outsole offers durable traction underfoot.

Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT Califia Aleali May (W)
results.story: The Aleali May x women’s Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort ‘Califia’ is drawn from a larger collection designed in partnership with the LA-based model and stylist. Inspired by May’s time with her high school drill team, the high-top features a leather upper in royal blue and pine green. Unique details include chenille Wings branding, an ‘A’ logo on the lace keeper and May’s signature engraved on the left heel. Additionally, green satin is utilized on the high-cut deconstructed collar and cut-out Swoosh. The rubber cupsole houses foam cushioning with a top-loaded Zoom Air unit for enhanced responsiveness.

adidas Ultra Boost 6.0 Halo Ivory (W)
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 6.0 ‘Halo Ivory’ delivers an understated colorway of a performance running shoe built with sustainability in mind. Neutral tan shades are applied to a Primeknit upper made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. Lightweight support and stability are provided by a midfoot cage and heel counter, both of which are constructed from recycled fishing nets retrieved from UK fishing quays. The sneaker rests on a full-length Boost midsole for springy cushioning with each step.
